The '''Naboo Underground''' was a [[Naboo Resistance|Resistance]] cell filled primarily by students from the [[Royal House of Learning/Legends|Royal House of Learning]]. It opposed the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]] during their [[Invasion of Naboo/Legends|occupation]] of [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]]. The group conducted several operations within the city of [[Theed/Legends|Theed]] during the occupation, and eventually joined forces with [[Padmé Amidala/Legends|Queen Amidala]] to participate in the [[Battle of Naboo/Legends|Second Battle of Theed]].

Many of the members worked together long after the Naboo's victory against the invasion.

==Operations==
The Naboo underground conducted a number of successful operations against the occupying forces, primarily involving weapons theft and liberation of prisoners. In one daring operation, they liberated the Naboo [[Minister of Culture/Legends|Minister of Culture]], [[Kyu Tane]].

While disbanded with the defeat of the Trade Federation during the [[Battle of Naboo/Legends|Battle of Naboo]], former members of the Naboo Underground played a key role in the defeat of the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]] organization the [[Renegade (organization)|Renegade]].

